### Smart Task - CollaborationController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs
@taskId = REPLACE_TASK_ID

### 1) Add comment (with mentions in content)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Please review this task @alice@example.com and @bob@example.com"
}

### 2) List comments by task
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Mock upload attachment (fake storage URL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/attachments/mock-upload
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="mock-spec.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test_api/files/mock-spec.pdf
--MyBoundary--

### 4) List attachments by task
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/attachments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Notes:
### - Mention parser reads emails after @ in comment content.
### - If you do not have a real file yet, create one: backend/prm_smart_task/test_api/files/mock-spec.pdf
### - Endpoint 3 does not upload to cloud; it returns a generated fake URL in fileUrl.
